headline: MarketAxess to Participate in the UBS Financial Services Conference
summary: NEW YORK, February 05, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced that Chris Concannon, Chief Executive Officer, and Ilene Fiszel Bieler, Chief Financial Officer, will participate in the UBS Financial Services Conference on February 10, 2025.
